        <item>
            <title>新疆成全球最大單體光伏項目併網發電，電量可供 300 萬户家庭使用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=worlds-largest-solar-plant</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:30:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[中國]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[全球最大單體光伏項目]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[新疆]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1241117</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">中國電力建設集團承建的新疆米東 3.5 吉瓦光伏項目第二標段工程於去年 8 月 29 日開始建設，早前宣佈成功併網。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1241139 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-694x391.jpg" alt="世界最大單體光伏項目" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1241143 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-1-694x391.jpg" alt="世界最大單體光伏項目" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-1-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant-goes-online-in-china-2/">pv magazine International</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">米東 3.5 吉瓦光伏項目拼網後年發電量可達 60.9 億 kWh，預計每年發電量足夠 300 萬户中國家庭使用，甚至能滿足盧森堡、巴布亞新幾內亞等小國整年的電力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1241144 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-2-694x391.jpg" alt="世界最大單體光伏項目" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-2-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-2.jpg 1052w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant-goes-online-in-china-2/">pv magazine International</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">這個全球最大單體光伏項目位於烏魯木齊市米東區北部沙漠，佔地約 20 萬畝，裝機容量為 3.5 吉瓦。米東 3.5 吉瓦光伏項目每年節約標準煤約 194.88 萬噸，減少二氧化碳排放量約 607.17 萬噸、煙塵約 165.65 萬噸、氮氧化合物約 91350 噸，遠遠優勝於同等規模的燃煤電廠，對加快當地能源結構優化和推動電力市場建設起了積極的作用。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20240606/s00004/1717652898056/%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e5%96%ae%e9%ab%94%e5%85%89%e4%bc%8f%e9%a0%85%e7%9b%ae%e4%bd%b5%e7%b6%b2%e7%99%bc%e9%9b%bb-%e6%af%8f%e5%b9%b4%e7%99%bc%e9%9b%bb%e9%87%8f%e8%b6%b3%e5%a4%a0300%e8%90%ac%e6%88%b6%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR1SWsBFMVIxfF_sh8eEkd_w54L9_hO39-EaJrePrCV_0A5u45O1i4ny4c0_aem_ARGHmmcVNAwFsnUsiWk_GxESUk_OxzkJRfQrGOACGJMfHFzEOtWXgufc90n38pBQLO_xzCFMJ6d1NpFEgKhAYzTl">明報</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant-goes-online-in-china-2/">pv magazine International</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/drone-mainland-china/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】到中國玩航拍必知 10 件事，註冊無人機 + 飛行高度距離 + 禁飛區 + 領牌制度</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/saudi-fund-invests-in-china-effort-to-create-rival-to-openai/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">沙特阿拉伯基金投資中國 AI　智譜 AI 獲注資 4 億美元</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/xi-bot/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國政府研發大模型應用　結合習近平思想作為知識庫</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant/fun-tech/">新疆成全球最大單體光伏項目併網發電，電量可供 300 萬户家庭使用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
